{{!
    @template tool_fix_delete_modules/task_diagnosis

    The template displays an explanation and an action button as part of a diagnosis for one course_delete_module task.

    Classes required for JS:
    * none

    Data attributes required for JS:
    * none

    Context variables required for this template:
    * description string - A sentence of text which describes the action to be taken when pressing the button.
    * fixbutton string - HTML form/button containing all form text needed to display the fix button.

    Example context (json):
    {
        "description": "This adhoc task contains multiple course modules so it is recommended to separate these into individual adhoc tasks.",
        "fixbutton": "<form>....</form>",
    }
}}
<div class="fix-diagnosis-action">
    <p>{{description}}</p>
    {{{fixbutton}}}
</div>
